{"tid":1385680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警稱示威者曱甴，爆市民頭係無所謂","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T19:38:58.000Z","uid":191740,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"263a055f18f8ccefbdf3e2c65dc6a34b7c509883","tid":1385680,"uid":191740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/30/144218_ff38dc2a1603850871e35e1deb34a110.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F30%2F144218_ff38dc2a1603850871e35e1deb34a110.png&h=461aec51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「他們(政府)只看你身分證的註記，你是圖西族(Tutsi)，代表是『該殺的』。」－盧安達事件倖存者喬瑟芬(Josephine)<br />\n<br />\n1994年4月7日，中非國家盧安達爆發種族內戰，佔85%人口的胡圖族(Hutu)人，聲稱要殺光佔14%的圖西族人。<span style=\"color: red;\">「在路上看到圖西族人，要像殺蟑螂一樣把他們除掉。」</span>該內戰在100天奪走至少80萬條生命，期間沒有任何國家伸出援手。直到10多年後，電影《盧安達大飯店》(Hotel Rwanda) 上映，才向以「民主、文明」為豪的人們投下震撼彈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cdn.org.tw/News.aspx?key=8104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdn.org.tw%2FNews.aspx%3Fkey%3D8104&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmIwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=711e4a33\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cdn.org.tw/News.aspx?key=8104</a>"},{"pid":"34aec6ce94d7645859be65c547e45c8a86d7a04d","tid":1385680,"uid":191740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:45:13.000Z","msg":"香港黑警向盧旺達暴政學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n軍政府不遠矣"},{"pid":"f5edfd778f7ae65b58a87c2bf54722f0b8bbc0d2","tid":1385680,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"咁黑警咪垃圾？<br />\n曱甴專食垃圾"},{"pid":"23685b409795bb35e12400d32c5559288eeb6858","tid":1385680,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:58:51.000Z","msg":"除暴GO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d82210032d33c79db74c5c74738c199856f400b","t